1159
01:35:22,420 --> 01:35:26,698
I already used all the explosives.

1160
01:35:26,780 --> 01:35:28,737
Or did I?

1161
01:35:30,460 --> 01:35:32,451
- I'm going to count to three.
- Yeah.

1162
01:35:32,540 --> 01:35:35,134
