1166
01:35:45,100 --> 01:35:47,979
[Yelling]

1167
01:36:08,620 --> 01:36:10,179
[Shouts In German]

1168
01:36:36,820 --> 01:36:39,778
Karl.

1169
01:36:39,860 --> 01:36:43,694
