and his family's home address...</i>

1179
01:38:17,900 --> 01:38:20,369
right here in L.A.

1180
01:38:20,460 --> 01:38:23,020
Whoa!

1181
01:38:23,100 --> 01:38:25,569
<i>[Elevator Bell Dings]</i>

1182
01:38:28,140 --> 01:38:29,938
<i>[Hans]
Go to work.</i>

1183
01:38:30,020 --> 01:38:32,011
Got it.

1184
01:38:44,060 --> 01:38:47,894
<i>God, that man looks really pissed.</i>

1185
01:38:49,460 --> 01:38:54,136
- He's still alive.
- What?

1186
01:38:54,220 --> 01:38:58,214
Only John can drive
somebody that crazy.

1187
01:38:59,700 --> 01:39:01,611
[Panting]

1188
01:39:01,700 --> 01:39:03,691
[Grunts]

1189
01:39:13,100 --> 01:39:15,774
