- <i>You don't want to know.</i>

1201
01:39:51,140 --> 01:39:54,770
Put me down for 20.
I'm good for it.

1202
01:39:54,860 --> 01:39:57,454
[Chuckling]

1203
01:39:57,540 --> 01:40:00,771
<i>Hey, Powell, you got flat feet?</i>

1204
01:40:02,900 --> 01:40:04,891
What the hell
you talking about, man?

1205
01:40:04,980 --> 01:40:07,893
