get you off the street.

1206
01:40:07,980 --> 01:40:10,494
<i>What's the matter? You don't think
jockeying papers across a desk...</i>

1207
01:40:10,580 --> 01:40:13,049
<i>is a noble effort for a cop?</i>

1208
01:40:14,540 --> 01:40:16,531
No.

1209
01:40:19,020 --> 01:40:22,900
- I <i>had an accident.</i>
<i>- The way you drive, I can see why.</i>

1210
01:40:23,020 --> 01:40:26,570
<i>What'd you do, run over
your captain's foot with a car?</i>

1211
01:40:29,700 --> 01:40:31,611
I shot a kid.

1212
01:40:33,420 --> 01:40:36,856
He was 13 years old.

1213
01:40:36,940 --> 01:40:39,329
